entry.title: redblood639/Treasury_Contract
entry.summary: This is a smart contract for managing a treasury that deposits funds into Uniswap and Aave. The contract allows the owner to set ratios for distribution between Uniswap and Aave, deposit USDC, and withdraw USDT and DAI.
